Description:
Don't localize Data Cube and ZONE 147.
A text string that appears on screen when the player attempts to open a door which is locked due to an emergency lockdown. Don't alter the RichText tags.

Italian.Translation: Trovare il cubo di dati [DATA_CUBE] nella <color=orange>ZONE 147</color>

Spanish.Translation: Encuentra el cubo de datos [DATA_CUBE] en la <color=orange>ZONE 147</color>.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Encontre o cubo de dados [DATA_CUBE] na <color=orange>ZONE 147</color>.

Japanese.Translation: <color=orange>ZONE 147</color>でデータキューブ[DATA_CUBE]を見つけろ
